<item>
            <title>[LU-11602] lfs find -i doesn&apos;t find directories with given stripe-offset in default file layout</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11602</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following doesn&apos;t find a directory that has a default file layout with stripe-offset set to 0:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lfs find -type d -i 0 /mnt/lustre&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reproduction:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;# mkdir /mnt/lustre/dir0
# lfs setstripe -i 0 /mnt/lustre/dir0
# touch /mnt/lustre/dir0/stripe0

# lfs find -type d -i 0 /mnt/lustre
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This should print &lt;tt&gt;/mnt/lustre/dir0&lt;/tt&gt;, but returns nothing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
